{"tid":1211772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩留意簽番兩項白宮聯署","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:39:13.000Z","uid":212998,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbaf8e318825027d70a00431233f98f1e303d24","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7NbjeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7NbjeQ.png&h=a132d970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依個post係特別比啲唔睇英文嘅人睇嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上面幅圖係錯嘅</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實兩個都係反送中嘅白宮聯署<br />\n<br />\n上面係希望取消有關送中官員嘅美國公民身份同簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill%3F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=55463e1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill?</a><br />\n<br />\n下面係要求白宮對負責香港送中條例的官員實施制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-sanctions-against-those-responsible-extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR1Wd-SiJR0_xABu_N2qpOwLnjre548CDbR2Gi5n_05TGtVKG7P3noB1CTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-sanctions-against-those-responsible-extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Wd-SiJR0_xABu_N2qpOwLnjre548CDbR2Gi5n_05TGtVKG7P3noB1CTI&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=4cf71c32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-sanctions-against-those-responsible-extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR1Wd-SiJR0_xABu_N2qpOwLnjre548CDbR2Gi5n_05TGtVKG7P3noB1CTI</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️麻煩兩個都要簽⚠️</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第兩項白官聯署先得2萬5人簽</span>"},{"pid":"e736a2bb1d733ca50c291f2f0b7a771692901e18","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97a974aea08a84a1aa30fdf9bcd57a515bbea10b","tid":1211772,"uid":142803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"623743c3fea6c2d50d9b93160822f401b041fe23","tid":1211772,"uid":62691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"簽完都唔會回應，簽黎做乜？"},{"pid":"1801c5f6416c73c74b2ea4cc95b81e5b6ef25407","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:42:52.000Z","msg":"比一比你身邊嘅朋友知<br />\n唔好淨係簽一個"},{"pid":"05de17a3fc0053073d508d03fa06e8fe56c89776","tid":1211772,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e52e678d6a8f19bd478acb64e852c625364c38be","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"623743c3fea6c2d50d9b93160822f401b041fe23","tid":1211772,"uid":62691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"簽完都唔會回應，簽黎做乜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:46:03.000Z","msg":"好過自己咩都唔做<br />\n然後被人當做支持送中嘅人"},{"pid":"819eb412cac6c09b81174afd6ebdfec1cf91fcf3","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73302a05dd9a41645e0c1208aaf1d1c0e0bbc6da","tid":1211772,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e52e678d6a8f19bd478acb64e852c625364c38be","tid":1211772,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"623743c3fea6c2d50d9b93